00:37:32.360 --> 00:37:36.360
fix things and to add features which are going to be used by millions of people.

00:37:38.280 --> 00:37:41.639
On the flip side, you start feeling a bit of responsibility for things

00:37:42.520 --> 00:37:46.679
and you become really attached to the things you've done.

00:37:48.600 --> 00:37:55.879
